      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore della variabile a zero               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-ipc-cod-pro-val      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     ipc-cod-pro-999.
       ipc-cod-pro-999.
